    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="title">
  <div class="inner_title">
   <div class="left">
        <h1>A global outlook on <br/>
        methane gas hydrates</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Undertaking an assessment of the state of the knowledge of methane gas hydrates</p>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/explore">EXPLORE THE SITES</a><span class="line"></span></li>
        <li><a href="/galleries">MEDIA RESOURCES</a><span class="line"></span></li>
        <li><a href="/events">UPCOMING EVENTS</a><span class="line"></span></li>
